About guile-gstreamer
===========================

guile-gstreamer contains the Guile wrappers for GStreamer, a
streaming-media framework.  It is a part of GNU guile-gnome, although it
is not part of the GNOME platform.

  http://gstreamer.freedesktop.org/
  http://gnu.org/s/guile-gnome/


Build dependencies
==================

guile-gstreamer requires GStreamer 0.10 development packages.

guile-gstreamer depends on guile-gnome-glib, which is commonly
distributed with the `guile-gnome-platform' tarball.  See
http://gnu.org/s/guile-gnome/, for more.


Copying guile-gstreamer
=====================

Distribution of guile-gstreamer is under the GPL.  See the COPYING file
for more information.


